<br>
I will note though that he is on a 10 minute timer, so if you need anything from the casters guild, simply pet up real quick and wax him, as I do everytime I see him <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> ..Wualla..you now have 10 minutes to get what you need as nothing else inside the guild is on that faction.  <br>
<br>
When you fight him, nothing will assist him.  Ive ran him all over the area and have yet to have anything help him as he died <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
